{"tid":2164982,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓貓眼框泛紅 可以點算？","createTime":"2020-08-19T13:41:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T13:47:47.000Z","uid":326428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1833cc9b80dcf9264c06a1ffcb743fa7fb479bb","tid":2164982,"uid":326428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T13:41:49.000Z","msg":"之前貓貓已經睇過醫生，食咗兩個星期藥，完成了療程，因為而家兩個月大多啲，打算星期六帶佢打針，但發現呢兩日眼睛又有少少問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尋日有黃綠色眼屎，但數量唔多，見到之後即刻都用返以前醫生比嘅消炎藥膏，之後眼睛就狀況好咗😭但係情況反覆，一到夜晚六點後就會紅，精神食嘢冇問題😭下圖係系貓貓狀況，以及用緊嘅藥膏。想問吓有冇人曾經都試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCKrW3o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCKrW3o.png&h=63744fb7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBG6cBO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBG6cBO.png&h=bee312b3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07a8d12e322080ad36bc7899a99946f16221f4cc","tid":2164982,"uid":59282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"試下食lysine? 我貓都會咁"},{"pid":"5496210ae336d8ac7fc44480c372812869a48178","tid":2164982,"uid":297655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:41:18.000Z","msg":"應該係皰疹病毒 我隻貓都有不過改善左好多<br />\n如果獸醫開普通感冒藥其實治標不治本 一轉環境/壓力就好易再爆<br />\n食lysine可以減低個病毒量 但要長期先有用<br />\n最緊要係照顧好佢正餐嘅營養同心理建康<br />\n<br />\n同埋<br />\n病緊唔好打針<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5216d852b13cd3caed6ec2ae4cdb921cfa1cc57","tid":2164982,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:17:12.000Z","msg":"Cat flu ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" cla